      },
      "source": [
        "## 3. Processing & feature engineering\n",
        "\n",
        "Three things need cleaning up before analysis:\n",
        "\n",
        "1. **Multi-select columns** (`ai_use`, `ai_want`, `ai_risk`) are stored as lists/arrays inside cells. We need a safe parser.\n",
        "2. **Survey wording is inconsistent** — e.g. `Organizing` (US) vs `Organising` (UK) for the same option. We map both to one canonical label.\n",
        "3. **Derived features** we'll use throughout: `not_using`, `n_uses`, `n_risks_flagged`, comfort buckets, an infrastructure score, and a labeled cluster name.\n",
        "\n",
        "### 3.1 Safe list parser"
      ]
    },
