      "source": [
        "### 5.2b The creative-to-operational flip\n",
        "\n",
        "The gap chart shows *which* use cases have the most unmet demand. This section makes the bigger point explicit: **current nonprofit AI use is mostly creative, while future nonprofit AI demand is mostly operational.**\n",
        "\n",
        "That is a meaningful shift in what the field is asking AI to do. Creative AI can often ride on consumer tools alone. Operational AI usually requires cleaner data, workflow integration, governance, and internal capacity.\n"
      ]
    },
