        "### 6.2 Insight #2: Conversion rate beats use/want gap\n",
        "\n",
        "The deck shows the use/want **gap**. A sharper framing is the **conversion rate**: among people who *want* a use case, what share are *already doing it*?\n",
        "\n",
        "This separates **felt-but-blocked** demand (low conversion) from **comfortable demand** (high conversion).\n",
        "\n",
        "| Use case            | Conversion |\n",
