      "source": [
        "### 8.3 Three novel insights\n",
        "\n",
        "#### Insight A — The \"AI Skeptic\" cluster is 93% mislabeled\n",
        "\n",
        "Of the 142 people in the published *AI Skeptic* cluster, only **10 (7%)** behaviorally fit the label. The plurality — 24% — are actually **Active Aspirants** (heavy AI users who want more). Another 11% are **Heavy Adopters**. The cluster lumps together at least eight distinct behavioral patterns under one misleading name."
      ]
