        "| \"High-comfort non-users abstain on principle\" | They're **Latent Adopters** — same comfort and aspiration as Heavy Adopters, but stalled on infrastructure. |\n",
        "\n",
        "The closer's punchline (*\"It's over infrastructure\"*) is now backed by behavior, not just stated attitudes.\n",
        "\n",
        "> **Bottom line for sector experts:** the published `cluster3` field is useful as a description of *aspiration*, but misleading as a description of *behavior*. Any program design that uses these clusters to identify who-needs-what should re-segment first.\n",
